      <title>Wireless weather Station</title>
      <link>/project/sensornetwork/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jul 2019 17:02:06 +0200</pubDate>
      <guid>/project/sensornetwork/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;During my postdoc at Uppsala University, I developed a prototype of a weather station to be used in a sensor network for urban energy and confort studies. The station is based on the LoRaWAN protocol, which provides  high range and low power consumption. A LAMP solution provides the storage of the sensor data and real-time monitoring.&lt;/p&gt;
